<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/10915875-suzanne"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1377997878i/10915875._UX100_CR0,16,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
