<span id="freeTextContainer17921804600457525870">This was a good read, a wholesome read! It was clean, uplifting and enjoyable. I really liked the story, including some of the &quot;wisdom of life&quot; comments and discussions that occur between Craneman and Tree Ear. I also appreciated the extra information and notes that the author included at the end to explain more about celadon pottery. I would definitely recommend this book!</span>
  <span id="freeText17921804600457525870" style="display:none">This was a good read, a wholesome read! It was clean, uplifting and enjoyable. I really liked the story, including some of the "wisdom of life" comments and discussions that occur between Craneman and Tree Ear. I also appreciated the extra information and notes that the author included at the end to explain more about celadon pottery. I would definitely recommend this book!</span>
