<span id="freeTextContainer6266128343338638231">#LitLife2for22 International Fiction <br/>What a beautiful story. Read it aloud to your kids or make sure they read it at some point. Wonderful plot and characters, excellent historical fiction, and such a unique setting. Made me cry.</span>

